The paper discusses the semantic labeling of 3D point clouds using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of deep learning also suggests that the paper may fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The focus on plant phenotyping suggests that the paper may also fall under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category, as this is a common application area for robotics in agriculture. Finally, the use of scanning and optimization techniques suggests that the paper may also fall under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
